<h1>IPG Management Solutions</h1>
<hr />
<p>IPG management solutions will provide an integrated management improvement solution based on IPG’s proprietary management model currently under development and being tested within IPG itself. The management solution involves novel work relationships, new techniques for management, and specially designed workspace. The goal of IPG management solution is to provide durable improvement to a company’s three fundamental winning factors: efficiency, innovation, and speed of knowledge transfer.</p>
